text: The Monroes was a 1960s American western series that ran for one season and 26 episodes on ABC. It ran from September 7, 1966 to March 15, 1967 and was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:American drama television series Category:Western (genre) television series Category:1966 television series debuts Category:1967 television series endings Category:English-language television programs Category:ABC network series
